content: I usually work from 9:00 am to 5:00 pm, with an hour lunch break from 12:00 pm to 1:00 pm. I try to fit in some exercise during my lunch break, like going for a 30-minute walk around the block. As for personal development, I've been reading a lot lately, usually around 9:30 pm before bed, and aim to do at least 30 minutes of reading per day.
